# Changelog

## 1.0 - 2018-04-19
- Change menu tags style
- Change app name
- Improve info text

## 0.5 - 2018-04-10
- Add website link to logo
- Change featured entries background and lines colors
- Reduce area of sidenav content

## 0.4 - 2018-02-16
- Improve info and contact text
- Add phones as a way of contact
- Update library version
- Use local fonts instead of CDN
- Set refresh time to 15 minutes
- Reduce sizes using minified javascripts and removing useless images

## 0.3 - 2018-02-13
- Show tags in entries list with color circles
- Show features news with a background color and bigger font size
- Beautify tags in menu
- Control network errors

## 0.2 - 2018-02-11 
- Logo corners rounded
- Improve info text
- Featured news pinned on top of the list

## 0.1 - 2018-02-09
- Initial release